channel.title: Changing spawn
channel.description:
Hello Moparscape Fourms, I am in need of help!
I was wondoring if anyone knew how to change this. When you create a new account you spawn in a certain location. If you know how to change that location please reply!
Thanks, The Astro

item.title: Changing spawn
item.dc:creator: @mr_bob_silab2 mr bob silab2
item.description:
@mr_bob_silab2 wrote:

Go into player.java and search for the current X cord of where you spawn. You will see the x and you will see it and the y cord below, change the cords to where you want to spawn then compile n run.
